00:11:57.950 --> 00:12:04.190
productive. And like for so Corinthians chapter 9 verse 26 says, we feel like we are making our

00:12:04.190 --> 00:12:14.110
blows count. If you're in the same situation as these publishers, what will you do now?

00:12:14.509 --> 00:12:23.070
Like Paul, we need to be willing to redirect our efforts based on the leadings of God's spirit.

00:12:24.350 --> 00:12:32.190
Learning another language may be one way that we can expand our ministry, but it's not the only way.

